title: Pink Floyd (1977) Animals
description:
One of my favourite albums that Roger Waters ever did.
David Gilmour's in there too (in the song Dogs).

I have most of the track data embedded in the files already, so your music players should go ahead and recognize it. I think the only thing i didn't put in there was the genre... because some people consider this Rock, others consider this Classic Rock, and there may be some other genres that i don't know about.

Enjoy!



Track 1: Pigs On The Wing (pt. 1)
Track 2: Dogs
Track 3: Pigs (Three Different Ones)
Track 4: Sheep
Track 5: Pigs On The Wing (pt. 2)
